<br>
Erikia <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uihaveasukhandle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ihaveasukhandle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>h0x0r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/4/02 8:08:40 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Help</span><hr size=1> casting skills/defense are maxed only thing that really matters to my knowledge. O and dodge is in the high 60's ;p <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/udonord.showPublicProfile?language=EN>donord</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>h0x0r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/4/02 9:19:47 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Help</span><hr size=1> what do you want us to say?  yay!  you have a 55 cleric you didn't work for?  thx info that's not gonna happen.<br>
