we all worked our asses off to get to where we are, we play the toughest class in the game and we do it mostly because no one else wants to.<br>
<br>
so don't assume we'll take pity and just ladeeda give you a magic formula, because there isn't one.  wanna learn to be a good cleric?  play, live, die, let others die, make mistakes, have lots of patience.<br>
<br>
shrug<br>
