<br>
Now, you also implied that the cleric you are getting isn't on Lanys.  Every server is diffrent.  I played a 58 cleric on Sullon Zek one night, and it took me a while to adjust to their 'lingo'  So, not only is just telling you how to play a high level cleric impossible, but telling you our 'lingo' won't do any good cause every server is diffrent.<br>
<br>
When you said you thought we'd be more helpful, we are trying to be, you just aren't listening to what we are saying.<br>
<br>
